org.encog.examples.nonlinear.tsp.genetic
Class SolveTSP

java.lang.Object
  org.encog.examples.nonlinear.tsp.genetic.SolveTSP

public class SolveTSP
extends Object

SolveTSP with a genetic algorithm. The Encog API includes a generic genetic algorithm problem solver. This example shows how to use it to find a solution to the Traveling Salesman Problem (TSP). This example does not use any sort of neural network.
